# Time Complexity

Suppose

```
n = Number of strings

k = Average length of each string
```

For every string

Convert to character array

```
O(k)
```

Sort

```
O(k log k)
```

Convert back to String

```
O(k)
```

Insert into HashMap

```
O(1)
```

Overall

```
O(n × k log k)
```

---

# Space Complexity

HashMap stores all strings.

```
O(n × k)
```

